Boca Juniors (ARG)            2-1 (2-1)     Real Madrid (ESP)
1-0 2' Martín Palermo
2-0 5' Martín Palermo
                                            2-1 11' Roberto Carlos

Boca Juniors:  Córdoba; Bermúdez, Traverso, Ibarra, Matellán; Basualdo,
               Serna, Riquelme, Battaglia (92' Burdisso); Delgado
               (87' Guillermo Barros Schelotto), Palermo.
               Coach: Carlos Bianchi.
Real Madrid:   Casillas; Hierro, Roberto Carlos, Karanka; McManaman
               (66' Savio), Luis Figo, Makelele (76' Morientes),
               Helguera, Guti, Geremi; Raúl.  Coach: Del Bosque.

yellow cards:  Ibarra (69'); Helguera (89'), Geremi (89')

Most valuable player of the match:  Martín Palermo (Boca Juniors)




